algorithm_technique: Brute-force generation of all possible decimal placements for x and y coordinates.
problem_summary_simple: Find all valid coordinate pairs from a string by inserting decimal points.
problem_summary_technical: Iterates through all possible split points for the string, generating valid decimal representations for x and y coordinates.
key_insights: The core challenge is to systematically explore all valid placements of decimal points.
Constraints on leading zeros and decimal point placement are crucial for filtering invalid possibilities.
The problem can be broken down into finding valid representations for the left and right parts of the coordinate.
